 hyperglycemia, and hyperinsulinemia are associated with a shift in cellular metabolism from lipid oxidation to TG esterification, thereby increasing the availability of TGs derived from VLDL synthesis and secretion.", "timestamp": "Fri May 15 21:31:46 +0000 2026"}